description:
Lightweight privacy-focused web browser
LibreLynx Lite is a lightweight, privacy-focused web browser for Android. It provides
  essential browsing features while prioritizing user privacy and minimal resource usage.

  Features:
    - Privacy-focused browsing
    - Lightweight and fast
    - Tab management
    - Bookmark support
    - History management
    - Multiple search engines
    - Theme customization
    - Swipe-to-refresh
